  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed roof extension and associated alterations, by reason of their inappropriate siting, scale, form, height, massing, bulk and prominence, would form a dominant and discordant addition to the existing characterful, legible and predominantly unaltered roofline of the host property and wider terrace. The extension would undermine the integrity of the terrace and would be clearly visible from short, medium and longer views from public and private viewpoints in and around the site. The proposal will fail to preserve and enhance the character and appearance of the Arlington Square Conservation Area contrary to the NPPF (2021), policies CS8 and CS9 of the Core Strategy (2011), policies DM2.1 and DM2.3 of the Development Management Policies (2013), the Islington Urban Design Guide (2017) and Islington's Conservation Area Design Guidelines (2002)."
